                     <interp inst="t18440205-757-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 coat, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 pair of gloves, 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 handkerchief, 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18440205-name-1288" type="victimName">
